msgid "To Do"
msgstr "المهام المراد تنفيذها"

#. module: carpenter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:carpenter.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To avoid double-counting costs and ensure an accurate profitability "
